                        <interp inst="t18460706-name-429" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH BENTON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 881.) I produce the certificate of the prisoner's former conviction from Mr. Clark's office—<hi rend="italic">—(read—Convicted the 3rd of Feb.</hi>, 1845, <hi rend="italic">and confined six months</hi>)—he is the person—he has been tried three times.</p>
